==English==

===Alternative spellings===
* [[defense]] (''US'')

===Noun===
'''defence'''
# the action of protecting from attack

====Quotations====
* '''1592&ndash;1609''': And nothing 'gainst Time's scythe can make '''defence''' /  Save breed, to brave him when he takes thee hence. &mdash; William Shakespeare, Sonnet XII
* '''1592&ndash;1609''': Speak of my lameness, and I straight will halt, / Against thy reasons making no '''defence'''. &mdash; William Shakespeare, Sonnet LXXXIX.

